A Mr Button b´aj t-xnaq´tza´n tuk´e jun t-xupin arco, extzen tzaj t-xo´n
t-xu´k t-xb´alun toj t-xu´k t-xu´k. Then he took out a sooty
tubo, n-nojsa´n tuk´e tabaco, extzen n-okx tq´o´n q´aq´ ti´j.
"Pawthrick," tzaj tq´ama´n jun tq´ajq´ajel wib´aj toj hamaca twitz, tzajni
aju n-ok t-xilen tqan, "ti t-xilen aju hilo n-chi tzyet tu´n t-xi t-xnaq´tzana
spin ter night 'bout a lip-me-dawn?"
"A alkye me-dawn?" xi tqanin Mr Button, n-chi tzaj t-xob´a twitz
t-xe t-xaq hamaca akux n-ok t-xo´n t-xmakal twitz t-xu´k.
