te n-chi b´ant ky-b´inchen aye bark t-xi´n ky-b´inchen ky-wa extzen tkyaqil; tze´nku
mya b´i´n wune ti n-ku q-k´amo´n toj bark. Aya, Jenkins, ti t-xilen
ma tz´okxa twitz atztzu?"
