bark?"
—Mi jun, chi Le Farge.
The unfortunate man's head sank on his breast. Nya nim ambʼil attoq te
tuʼn t-ximen kyiʼj nya bʼaʼn in che tzaj tiʼj, noqtzun tuʼnj, tuʼnju in xi tzyet jun nya bʼaʼn
