Otaq tzʼok qʼij toj juntl qʼij. A bark nim twa´l t-xi´ t-xo´n tib´aj a´. A
aju b´ajsb´il t-xaq a´ otoq txi q´o´n wajxaq or t-xe.
A bark te tmij, ikyx tze´n jun nya b´a´n t-xilen, otaq tz´ok t-xob´il extzen
in che ok lpe' ti'j tkyaqil q'ij, in che qanin a' ex minti'toq a'. A
iktoq tten ik tzeʼn qe naʼj Dios jaku kubʼ t-ximen jun xjal tuʼn tok tbʼiʼn toj infierno.
Aye xjal ate´ toj bark nim twa´lil, b´isb´ajil ex b´isb´ajil, n-chi tzaj ky-b´is tuk´e
jun tnab´l il, n-ok yajb´il tu´n nik´aj a´, extzen n-ok yajb´il tu´n tq´ajq´ajel twi´
n-chi qaninte a´, n-chi kub´ ky-q´o´n kyib´aj ky-remos tej t-xi t-ximan juntl bark
tu’n tpon laq’e’.
Jalin extzun, noq minab´en, extzen ikyjo tze´nku n-chi b´et tu´n jun ky-xim,
kykyaqil n-chi ẍch´in junx: "Minti´ jun qeye." Extzun aye
jun kwart-bark mya n-xi tnimen. Noqx tajb´en tu´n t-xi ttzyu´n aju´ t-xaq
tuk´e aju´ bung tun t-xi yek´unte t-xew, aju´ tmij-delirious
aye txuk tzaj ky-ximan toj ky-wi´x qa aye ky-xjalil
n-chi tzaj t-xmoxin kye a´ mya at.
Ik tza´n t-xi´ t-xo´n q´ij twitz mar, a Lestrange, n-jaw we´ twitz
jun torpor jatumel otoq tz´okx tz´aq, jaw t-xo´n tib´ ex xi tka´yin twitz
a gunwale. Ok tq´o´n twitz ti´j bark te kwart n-chi b´et t-xilen jun cable
najchaq, n-chi qoptz´aj tu´n tkyaqil t-spik´umal q´ij, extzen aye t-xew, n-chi ka´yin
te, n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n toj jun t-xilen ky-tzi´ ky-q´eq.
